msgstr "Tasemete redaktor"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kgoldrunner.appdata.xml:22
msgid ""
"Two modes for the enemies: classical and KGoldrunner-mode, in KGoldrunner-"
"mode they are more intelligent, in the classical mode it is easier to fool "
"them"
msgstr ""
"Kaht tüüpi vaenlased: klassikalised ja KGoldrunneri omad. KGoldrunneri "
"vaenlased on nupukamad, klassikalisi on küllaltki hõlpus ninapidi vedada"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
